dc_description_s: This point dataset shows the locations of oilseed processing plants in the United States for 2015. This layer is a part of a collection of GIS data containing renewable and electric energy information for the U.S., including data on transmission lines, power plants and electricity substations. This shapefile can be used to locate and analyze existing Oilseed Processing Plants used in the developemtn of Biodiesel. Hart Energy Publishing. (2015) Oilseed processing plants: United States, 2015. Hart Energy Publishing. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/nt296kt2309 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
